    {
      "id": "6a0a86a9631bea7100ad0ba5",
      "text": "一日一文",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779074732,
      "updated": 1779074732
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a86aa00000000008f545a",
      "text": "[hiro.icon] [一日一文 https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/5B28-6184]",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779074732,
      "updated": 1779074733
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0a86ac00000000008f545b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779074733,
      "updated": 1779074733
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae3c8000000000028dde3",
      "text": " 私の[日課]エッセー（[希哲館訳語]：越省）[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098593,
      "updated": 1779098617
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae3c9000000000028dde4",
      "text": "  もともと[デルン]上で1日1文章を書こうという日課「一日一章」として2014年に始めた（[一日一章の心がけ https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/A99F]）",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098594,
      "updated": 1779099392
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae539000000000028dde9",
      "text": "   いまいち続かず",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098962,
      "updated": 1779098970
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae435000000000028dde7",
      "text": "  妙にやる気を出して一日十章、一日八章などとしていた時期もあった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098702,
      "updated": 1779099208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae532000000000028dde8",
      "text": "   当然続かず",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098954,
      "updated": 1779098957
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae574000000000028ddea",
      "text": "  2019年に「一日一文」に",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779099021,
      "updated": 1779099029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae59b000000000028ddeb",
      "text": "   日課としてもっと気軽な感じにしようと思った",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779099060,
      "updated": 1779099068
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae5e6000000000028ddec",
      "text": "  様々な試行錯誤を経て2026年現在",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779099135,
      "updated": 1779099405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae5f9000000000028dded",
      "text": "   [『希哲日記』 https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/4686-E8CF]の一部となった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779099154,
      "updated": 1779099174
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae40a000000000028dde6",
      "text": "   雑文程度のものから、より内面的なエッセーという位置付けに",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098659,
      "updated": 1779099416
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae636000000000028ddee",
      "text": "   長年の試行錯誤で、毎日それなりの文章を書き上げるなんて出来ることではないと悟ったので、1日1文章の書き上げを努力目標として、毎日30分文章執筆に時間をあてる日課になっている",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779099215,
      "updated": 1779099343
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0ae3e2000000000028dde5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779098619,
      "updated": 1779098619
    }
  ]
}